<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="description" content="Basic HTML5 Document" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="HTML5, Responsive" />
    <title>Your Wholesome Dose</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hedvig+Letters+Serif:opsz@12..24&family=Mooli&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <style>
      html {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #add8e6, #ffb6c1, #e6e6fa);
        background-size: cover;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        height: 100%;
      }
      body {
        font-family: "Hedvig Letters Serif", serif;
      }
      #heading {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 4rem;
        border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */
        color: crimson;
      }
      p {
        color: #000080;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      ul {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      button {
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: black;
        border: 2px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px #aaa;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: box-shadow 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        color: #c8a2c8;
        font-family: "Hedvig Letters Serif", serif;
      }
      button:hover {
        box-shadow: 4px 4px 10px crimson;
        transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
      }
      #buttons_info_entry {
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      a {
        color: crimson;
      }
      #button-container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        margin: 20px;
      }

      .wholesome-button {
        border: none;
        background-size: contain;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        width: auto; /* Width will adjust to the content */
        height: 200px; /* Set a fixed height, or adjust as needed */
        background-position: center;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: bolder;
        color: #c8a2c8;
      }
      #cat{
        background-image: url(./Images/cat.jpg)
      }
      #end{
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="heading">
        Welcome To Your Daily Dose of Wholesomeness
    </div>
    <p id="welcome_message">Hey there, random doodle-o! Thank you for taking out time to visit us. The website's goal is to provide you with your daily dose of wholesomeness which you might be missing out on.</p>
    <p id="step_1_message">To begin you have two options:</p>
    <ul id="option_list_id">
      <div id="buttons_info_entry">
        <button><b><em>If you already are a part of the community then, please log in:<a href="wholesomeoverload.onrender/logIN">      logIn</a></em></b></button>
        <button><b><em>If you're a new user, please sign up:<a href="wholesomeoverload.onrender/sign_up">      signUp</a></em></b></button>
      </div>
    </ul>
    <p>Fantastic! We have gathered all the necessary elements we needed to meet the requirements. Simply click the button below, that interests you the most and enjoy the wholesome dynamic transitions</p>
    <div id="button-container">
      <button class="wholesome-button" id="cat"><a href="wholesomeoverload.onrender/cat"><em><b>CATS OVERLOAD</b></em></a></button>
    </div>
    <p id="end">We intend to add more content in the future but for now this is all we have ^__^</p>
  </body>
</html>
